{"tid":223490,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 - 原來麥樂雞新鮮熱辣唔係最好食","createTime":"2017-04-30T11:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T12:30:40.000Z","uid":74981,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47e5888776119a65ab54f6c7ef5e06e87c931a47","tid":223490,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/4c11b73f1f8ab8e7ee8f23ae73893bae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F4c11b73f1f8ab8e7ee8f23ae73893bae.jpg&h=6edd55c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前買18件食剩左幾舊，放入雪櫃，擺左4日，突然想清左去，於是用少少油煎左佢，點知原來咁搞法會超脆口，脆過平時M記炸，又熱辣辣，正到暈，以後買麥樂雞都唔即刻食，放係雪櫃幾日先拎番出黎煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebb77c09ddb76f8d7ca2588d9542474e08fa154","tid":223490,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"食屎"},{"pid":"7eb934951403cac2e75a9975bfaa3b3dec2b0dc1","tid":223490,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:17:27.000Z","msg":"咪癲啦"},{"pid":"37222ccb05ec8895ca1dddfe728594729e3936f9","tid":223490,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e04e13f2ad9ae158ce0d57041afb44bddf35dd9f","tid":223490,"uid":97179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"煎黑左梗係脆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ee221357a19587910ee1f180998bf10e805e6f","tid":223490,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"攞去餵狗"},{"pid":"8ddadf5503cd9f3c391fc3e954e0eb184789c70a","tid":223490,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"唔使擺入雪櫃都唔會發霉呀"},{"pid":"fbaf02ccccba7049a12528d703d0d28abda8ae47","tid":223490,"uid":28031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"